snippet.title: Underhell Chapter 1 Trailer
snippet.description:
Underhell Chapter 1 Trailer has arrived! It features a lot of voices from many different conversations throughout the game.
This should give you an idea of what to expect as far as ambient and immersion are concerned.

Enjoy.

Mod DB Page : http://www.moddb.com/mods/underhell

Website : http://underhell.wecreatestuff.com/

Steam Community Page : http://steamcommunity.com/groups/Underhell

Personal Website : http://www.mxthe.com/
